column5: well went out for the first time on Saturday with my friends Janine, mark and Kim. some perch was caught by all three of them. but i was the winner of the day with one 43 inch muskie 17.1 lbs. on a orange jig head with an off white grab.  and a 20 inch walleye same jig head.
sorry for the two reports was having trouble uploading the pictures. once i resize them. it work the pictures showed up. happy fishing, see you on the water  walleyedreamer
Nice catch. Too bad the pictures are a little small though.  Try hosting your fish at photobucket dot com. I dont even resize the pictures.
i work on that johnnybass next time i try to make them biger. happy fishing, see you on the water, walleyedreamer
